# Firestore Security

- Users read/write only their `users/{uid}` doc or same-family data.
- `familyId` on writes must match the caller's family.
- Never trust client-side overlap validation as authoritative.
- Deploy rules before testing multi-user flows.

Load `.cursor/skills/platform/firebase/SKILL.md` and `references/collections-and-rules.md` for rules changes.
